OS : Ubuntu 12.04 and greater


1. Install odt2html

	sudo apt-get install unoconv

2. Install python-wordpress-xmlrpc

    Verify you meet the following requirements:

            WordPress 3.4+ OR WordPress 3.0-3.3 with the XML-RPC Modernization Plugin.
            Python 2.6+ OR Python 3.x

    Install from PyPI using easy_install python-wordpress-xmlrpc or pip install python-wordpress-xmlrpc.

	sudo apt-get install python-pip
	sudo easy_install python-wordpress-xmlrpc



